    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/9fba6387c796bac0ba0416e0af5e9c36.avif?t=1734628470\" width=616 height=350 /></span>欢迎莅临这颗星球，我们真诚希望你能够在这颗星球，探索到专属的……绚丽多彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请携带好随身探索物品，即将进入地下世界开启一场探索之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请勿随意将头手伸出防护服，那将可能对造成不必要的影响；部分奇异炫光植物可随意触碰或采摘，希望它们能对你有所帮助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若在探索过程中发现了任何异常，请及时与我们联系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可要千万当心，这儿可不是一颗普通的星球！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/cdbcd4781546dd014c383e329c96612b.poster.avif?t=1734628470\" width=616 height=179 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/cdbcd4781546dd014c383e329c96612b.webm?t=1734628470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挖掘！不断挖掘！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向哪里挖？凭着你的第六感，朝着资源最丰富的矿脉，挥动锄头！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过挖掘能找到各种矿石材料，隐藏的山洞充满惊喜，还能解锁更加先进的自动化组件，甚至……生产线上卡脖子的技术方案也有可能通过这种方式解决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/a8148e69aa47a17d89e9cba39ff4f750.poster.avif?t=1734628470\" width=616 height=179 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/a8148e69aa47a17d89e9cba39ff4f750.webm?t=1734628470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >采集，解锁，建造。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地底找寻到各种各样的装备，利用你采集到的资源解锁那些尘封的生产工具。装上合适的工具，建造机器来解放双手，再往深处继续探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个星球大得超乎想象，资源更是丰富多样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果地势不符合你的要求，或挖掘或使用科技力量重建整块地势，超高自由度造你所想！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/65d58877300fb38769d12a32de23b4fe.poster.avif?t=1734628470\" width=616 height=179 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/65d58877300fb38769d12a32de23b4fe.webm?t=1734628470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自动化生产，就是最终目的吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不，这只是其中关键的一步罢了。把生产线延伸到洞穴尽头，将这里打造成你的流水线生产基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有传送带和机械臂，它们能助你事半功倍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对了，别忘了反复调校一下产线上的机器，你的工厂生产效率还能再提高些！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/caac0f59fdc581001e06032acefbdbc6.poster.avif?t=1734628470\" width=616 height=179 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457320/extras/caac0f59fdc581001e06032acefbdbc6.webm?t=1734628470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>工号4587的探索者，您的伙伴发来了一条信息，是否现在查看？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >”朋友，我总觉得这里不对劲。“</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >”小心！！&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索者们，在这个星球上掉以轻心可是大忌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于这款游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 这不是一个纯探索建造游戏，请在游玩时务必留心身边一切可疑的事物，它们都是线索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从手动收集到自动化生产，游戏中将为您提供了多种升级方案，一切更快更高效地生产</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果觉得个人探索建造太肝了，星核工厂支持至多四人在线，人一多肝儿也就保住了</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索过程中，不仅有语音向导陪你唠嗑，一系列原创配乐，保证你的探索之旅无比惬意</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
